Pega Capital Resources Ltd &lt;PGA.TO> saidit agreed in principle to acquire a 50 pct undivided interestin all rights and patents to a tamper resistant andtamper-evident packaging process for 1,250,000 dlrs.    The company said the purchase price is payable in 1,250,000common shares priced at one dlr each. The shares will be paidunder an escrow agreement where Pega may terminate the purchaseagreement and cancel the shares up to October 31, 1987.    It said the process results in readily visible breakage ifpackaging material is pierced by a sharp object. Reuter&#3;